attributes.description: This dashboard shows Alert collected by the Flashpoint Integration.

params.markdown:
This dashboard provides centralized visibility into alerts generated by Flashpoint.

It includes a pie chart showing Alerts by Data Types and a control panel highlighting Source and Origin. Alert activity over time is visualized through a line chart, while tables present Top Authors and Top MIME Types. A bar chart displays Alerts by Sources, and a key metric highlights the Total Alerts. Geographic distribution of alert-related resources is shown using a map of Top Resource Countries.

Together, these visualizations help teams quickly monitor alert trends and investigate alert sources and content.

**[Integration Page](/app/integrations/detail/ti_flashpoint)**
